<script>
  (function() {
  // Cross-browser matchMedia change event support
  function addColorSchemeListener(handler) {
    var mediaQuery = window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)');
    // Modern browsers
    if (mediaQuery.addEventListener) {
      mediaQuery.addEventListener('change', handler);
    }
    // Legacy browsers (Safari 13, IE)
    else if (mediaQuery.addListener) {
      mediaQuery.addListener(handler);
    }
    return mediaQuery;
  }

  // Color mapping
  var darkModeMap = [
    { from: "rgb(255, 255, 255)", to: "#222" },
    { from: "rgb(17, 17, 17)", to: "#eee" },
    { from: "rgb(102, 102, 102)", to: "#bbb" },
    { from: "rgb(164, 164, 164)", to: "#888" },
    { from: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06)", to: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06)" }
  ];
  var lightModeMap = [
    { from: "#222", to: "rgb(255, 255, 255)" },
    { from: "rgb(34, 34, 34)", to: "rgb(255, 255, 255)" },
    { from: "#eee", to: "rgb(17, 17, 17)" },
    { from: "rgb(238, 238, 238)", to: "rgb(17, 17, 17)" },
    { from: "#bbb", to: "rgb(102, 102, 102)" },
    { from: "rgb(187, 187, 187)", to: "rgb(102, 102, 102)" },
    { from: "#888", to: "rgb(164, 164, 164)" },
    { from: "rgb(136, 136, 136)", to: "rgb(164, 164, 164)" },
    { from: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06)", to: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06)" }
  ];

  // Apply color mappings to all page elements
  function applyColorScheme(isDark) {
    var map = isDark ? darkModeMap : lightModeMap;
    document.querySelectorAll('*').forEach(function(element) {
      var style = window.getComputedStyle(element);

      // Color
      var currentColor = style.color;
      var mapped = map.find(function(m) { return m.from === currentColor; });
      if (mapped) {
        element.style.color = mapped.to;
      }

      // Background Color
      var bgColor = style.backgroundColor;
      var mappedBg = map.find(function(m) { return m.from === bgColor; });
      if (mappedBg) {
        element.style.backgroundColor = mappedBg.to;
      }
    });
  }

  // Handler to run on color scheme change or page load
  function updateColors() {
    var isDark = window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches;
    applyColorScheme(isDark);
  }

  // Listen for scheme changes and update immediately
  var mediaQuery = addColorSchemeListener(updateColors);
  // Also update on load
  updateColors();
})();

  // Function to add underline-on-hover CSS for all elements with href attribute
  function addLinkHoverUnderline() {
    // Create a style element
    var style = document.createElement('style');
    style.textContent = `
      [href]:hover {
        text-decoration: underline !important;
        text-underline-offset: 3px;
        cursor: pointer;
      }
    `;
    document.head.appendChild(style);
  }

  // Run the function on page load
  addLinkHoverUnderline();
</script>
